----------------
bunker roof test site for PST-experiments in Fl&#252;elatal, close to creek, shady, sheltered, sun finally reaches the valley bottom again for about 20 mins around noon

PROFILE
-------
only upper part of interest recorded, lower part mix of crusts, melt forms and rounded facets,
TG low because of location on the roof with cold temps in the bunker below

COMMENT
-------
PSTs tested on SH layer 62-62.5 cm, results were not satisfying, even on tilted experiments up to slope = 25 deg
Upper part of the snowpack shoveled of for the tests (97.5 cm upwards), density only measured for slab with cylinder (4 measurements for each intervall)</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2022-02-10T11:15:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2022-02-11T08:22:57.987000+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2022-02-11T08:48:57.495000+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Davos -  Bunker Fl&#252;elastrasse</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>1640</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>0</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.869968 46.807726</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">115.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-6.6</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">115.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">1.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>SH</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>2.0</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>6.0</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">1.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">16.0</caaml